---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Tax Preparation in Las Vegas – Guzman Tax Accounting" description="Professional tax preparation in Las Vegas. 1040, LLC, S-Corp. Bilingual staff. We maximize your refund." lang="en" langHref="/taxes">
<section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/en/">Home</a> <span>›</span> <span>Tax Preparation</span></div><h1>Tax Preparation</h1><p>Personal and business tax returns. Bilingual service. We maximize your refund legally.</p></div></section>
<section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="mission-grid">
  <div class="mission-content"><p class="eyebrow">Why Choose Us?</p><h2>Stress-Free Taxes, In Your Language</h2><p>Tax season does not have to be complicated. Our team has years of experience preparing returns for individuals, families and businesses in Las Vegas.</p>
    <div class="mission-points">
      <div class="mission-point"><div class="mission-point-icon">✓</div><div class="mission-point-text"><h4>1040 – Personal Return</h4><p>W-2, 1099, interest, dividends and more. We maximize every legal deduction.</p></div></div>
      <div class="mission-point"><div class="mission-point-icon">✓</div><div class="mission-point-text"><h4>Business – LLC, S-Corp, C-Corp</h4><p>Complete corporate returns with tax strategy included.</p></div></div>
      <div class="mission-point"><div class="mission-point-icon">✓</div><div class="mission-point-text"><h4>ITIN for Undocumented Individuals</h4><p>We help you obtain your ITIN and file correctly, regardless of immigration status.</p></div></div>
      <div class="mission-point"><div class="mission-point-icon">✓</div><div class="mission-point-text"><h4>Prior Years</h4><p>Did not file previous years? We help you catch up without problems.</p></div></div>
    </div>
    <a href="/en/free-consultation" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:24px;">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
  </div>
  <div><img src="/assets/taxes-banner.png" alt="Tax Preparation Las Vegas" style="border-radius:16px;width:100%;" loading="lazy"/>
    <div style="margin-top:24px;background:var(--gray);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;"><h4 style="margin-bottom:14px;">What Documents Do You Need?</h4><ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text-light);"><li>✓ Form W-2 or 1099</li><li>✓ Social Security Number or ITIN</li><li>✓ Valid ID</li><li>✓ Prior year return (if applicable)</li><li>✓ Dependent information</li></ul></div>
  </div>
</div></div></section>
<section class="cta-section"><div class="container"><h2>Check Your IRS Refund</h2><p>Already filed and want to know the status of your refund? The IRS has an official tool.</p><div class="btn-group"><a href="https://www.irs.gov/refunds" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Check at IRS.gov</a><a href="/en/free-consultation" class="btn btn-white">Schedule Free Consultation</a></div></div></section>
</Layout>
